OL,3,CMembers of people smuggling network
OL,4,Csentenced over small boat crossing
OL,6,FNine members of a people smuggling
OL,7,Fnetwork have been sentenced over a
OL,8,Fsmall boat crossing which left four
OL,9,Fpeople dead and another four missing.
OL,11,FSeven Afghan nationals and two Iraqis
OL,12,Fwere convicted of offences including
OL,13,Finvoluntary manslaughter, endangering
OL,14,Flives and facilitating illegal entry
OL,15,Ffollowing a trial in Lille, northern
OL,16,FFrance.
OL,18,FOne of the men was tried in his
OL,19,Fabsence after fleeing France before
OL,20,Ftrial.
