OL,3,CMembers of people smuggling network
OL,4,Csentenced over small boat crossing
OL,6,FThe judge handed the Afghan ringleader
OL,7,Fof the gang an eight-year jail term.
OL,9,FThe others were sentenced to seven
OL,10,Fyears each.
OL,12,FIt followed a criminal investigation,
OL,13,Fsupported by the National Crime Agency
OL,14,F(NCA), into an incident on 14 December
OL,15,F2022, when a boat carrying 47 people
OL,16,Fgot into trouble in the English
OL,17,FChannel.
OL,19,FFour people were confirmed to have
OL,20,Fdied and another four were never found.
