OL,6,FThe survivors were rescued by a
OL,7,FBritish fishing vessel and brought to
OL,8,Fshore in Dover.
OL,10,FThe NCA and Kent Police worked with
OL,11,Fthe French authorities to identify
OL,12,Fthose responsible for putting the boat
OL,13,Fin the water.
OL,15,FThey provided crucial intelligence and
OL,16,Fevidence to French investigators
OL,17,Fincluding interviews with the
OL,18,Fsurvivors.
