OL,4,Csentenced over small boat crossing
OL,6,FSenegalese national Ibrahima Bah, 20,
OL,7,Fwas later convicted in the UK of
OL,8,Fpiloting the boat.
OL,10,FHis trial, at Canterbury Crown Court,
OL,11,Fheard how the "death trap" dinghy was
OL,12,Fheavily overloaded, and only had space
OL,13,Ffor around 20 people.
OL,15,FMany of those on board did not have
OL,16,Flife-jackets.
OL,18,FHe was jailed for nine years in
OL,19,FFebruary 2024.
