OL,3,CMembers of people smuggling network
OL,4,Csentenced over small boat crossing
OL,6,FNCA Deputy Director Rick Jones said:
OL,7,F"This was a tragic event which sadly
OL,8,Fdemonstrated the extreme danger
OL,9,Finvolved in putting overloaded boats
OL,10,Finto the sea.
OL,12,F"While our thoughts remain with the
OL,13,Floved ones of those who died, I'm glad
OL,14,Fthat those who organised this crossing
OL,15,Fhave now been brought to justice.
OL,17,F"The gangs involved in this type of
OL,18,Fcriminality have no concern for the
OL,19,Fwelfare or safety of those they
OL,20,Ftransport, they're just in it for the
OL,21,Fmoney.
